This is my Mom (the rock of our family) and in March of 2019 she was diagnosed with Stage 4 breast cancer.  I shared her story and her fight on the first season of the Challenge All Stars where you guys got to see her during my phone calls home.  I always get asked how she is doing and how’s she feeling.
Well although fighting cancer is a very painful battle and to be honest sucks, she is still fighting each day. She’s now going into her 5th year of fighting and she wanted to thank everyone for the kind words and prayers🙏🏼🙏🏼🙏🏼 Thank you to everyone that has had my Mom in their thoughts.  Keep fighting Mom I love you ❤️ #FuckCancer #LongStrong
